      <title>市场实时动态：各国央行的降息空间比想象的要小吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-07/c-banks-have-less-headroom-to-cut-than-thought-mliv-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储、欧洲央行和英国央行均无法降息，因为通胀仍未完全被抑制，彭博策略师 Ven Ram 与 Guy Johnson 和 Tom Mackenzie 在“彭博今日市场”节目中进行了讨论。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-07/c-banks-have-less-headroom-to-cut-than-thought-mliv-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 09:23:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
