      <title>欧洲央行首选薪资指标在新的通胀警告中加速上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/ecb-s-preferred-pay-gauge-accelerates-in-new-inflation-warning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行首选的欧元区薪资衡量指标在 2024 年初显示出加速增长，这是该地区价格压力依然顽固的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/ecb-s-preferred-pay-gauge-accelerates-in-new-inflation-warning</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 09:05:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国央行停止为期 18 个月的黄金购买狂潮，黄金价格暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/china-s-pboc-halts-gold-purchases-after-price-hits-record-in-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行上个月没有购买任何黄金，结束了持续 18 个月的大规模购买狂潮，并推动黄金价格在 5 月份创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/china-s-pboc-halts-gold-purchases-after-price-hits-record-in-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 08:06:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>薪资上涨​​，欧洲央行官员对进一步降息持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/ecb-s-kazaks-says-any-further-rate-cuts-need-to-be-gradual</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在薪资压力依然巨大的情况下，欧洲央行官员对进一步降息持谨慎态度，其中一位官员甚至表示，进一步降息的可能性不大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/ecb-s-kazaks-says-any-further-rate-cuts-need-to-be-gradual</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 05:44:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度储备银行维持利率不变，等待新莫迪政府上台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/india-central-bank-keeps-rates-steady-as-modi-coalition-awaited</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正如预期的那样，印度央行维持基准利率不变，在意外选举结果导致政策不确定性的情况下继续关注通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/india-central-bank-keeps-rates-steady-as-modi-coalition-awaited</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 04:34:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯有望从阿美石油出售中获得 112 亿美元收益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/aramco-sale-set-to-raise-at-least-11-2-billion-for-saudi-arabia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿美公司的大规模股票发行将为利雅得筹集至少 112 亿美元，这是约三年来全球最大的此类交易，将有助于为数万亿美元的经济转型计划提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/aramco-sale-set-to-raise-at-least-11-2-billion-for-saudi-arabia</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 00:07:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
